                <td class="chblue"><font class="h1font"> Intermediate Decks</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3"><tr><td><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Hyren&#39;s Favor</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(2.33)</font> | <A HREF="/magination/decks/decks.php?reviews=22510">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=10047">Matthew "Matofacus" Seavey</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=10047&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Use Tony Jones, Yerth, and Yaki to unleash the awsome power of the almighty Hyren!</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> March 31, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Magi:<br>
Yerth<br>
(Starting: Any one Hyren, <a href="javascript:card_browser(510)">Staff of Hyren</a>)<br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(514}<a href="javascript:card_browser({901)">Tony</a> Jones</a><br>
(Starting: Any one Creature, <a href="javascript:card_browser(400)">Furok</a>)<br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(416)">Yaki</a><br>
(Starting: Arbol, <a href="javascript:card_browser(400)">Furok</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(409)">Weebo</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(423)">Grow</a>)<br>
<br>
Creatures:<br>
